"'''High Sparrow'''"<ref>[http://watchersonthewall.com/first-three-episode-titles-game-thrones-season-5-revealed/]</ref> is the third episode of the [[Season 5|fifth season]] of ''[[Game of Thrones]]''. It is the forty-third episode of the series overall. It will premiere on April 26, 2015. It was directed by [[Mark Mylod]].
sections.Notes: *The episode title is a reference to the [[High Sparrow]], a new character introduced this season.
